  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> lean beef mince</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong> to a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Using clean hands, give everything a very good mix up until fully combined</p><p>Divide the <strong>lean beef mixture</strong> into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20] </span>and roll into meatballs</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
