            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> meatballs</strong> and cook for 2 min, turning occasionally, until browned</p><p>Once browned, transfer the<strong> </strong>meatballs to a plate and set aside</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
